	    <p class="area-detail">We can help you negotiate a purchase and sales agreement, address title issues, and prepare or review closing documents.</p>
	    <p class="area-detail">We also have extensive knowledge of real estate in the probate arena.  If you inherited a house, inherited a share of a house or have an interest in a house held in trust or in common with another individual, we can help you understand your rights and guide you toward a viable resolution.</p>

